                     <interp inst="t18670408-407-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing one watch, one chain, and one locket of <persName id="t18670408-name-306" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18670408-name-306" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670408-name-306" type="surname" value="JACOBS"></interp>
