                        <interp inst="t18670408-407-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted in August, 1865, in the name of Robert Nash, to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
